        "common:generalComment": [
          {
            "@xml:lang": "en",
            "#text": "  Mass*distance is a composite physical quantity for transport service workload.\n  Reference unit: kg·km (kilogram-kilometer)\n  Primarily applied in environmental impact assessment of logistics processes.\n  Not applicable for substance properties, only for functional/service flow quantification."
          },
          {
            "@xml:lang": "zh",
            "#text": "  质量*距离是复合物理量，用于描述运输服务的工作量。\n  基准单位：kg·km（千克公里）\n  主要应用于物流运输过程的环境影响评估。\n  不适用于描述物质本身的属性，仅用于功能单位或服务流的量化。"
